vormen = vierkant, driehoek, cirkel, zeshoek, ster, ruit, ovaal
color white
forward 200
turn -90
forward 275
turn 180
for computerkeuze in vormen
    eigenkeuze = ask 'De computer wil een ' computerkeuze ' tekenen, wat wil jij tekenen? (vierkant, driehoek, cirkel, zeshoek, ster, ruit, ovaal of Enter)'
    if eigenkeuze in vormen
        vormkeuze = eigenkeuze
    else
        vormkeuze = computerkeuze
    kleurkeuze = ask 'Kies een kleur (rood, blauw, groen, geel, oranje, paars) of laat de computer kiezen'
    if kleurkeuze = rood
        color red
    if kleurkeuze = blauw
        color blue
    if kleurkeuze = groen
        color green
    if kleurkeuze = geel
        color yellow
    if kleurkeuze = oranje
        color orange
    if kleurkeuze = paars
        color purple
    else
        color kleuren at random
    if vormkeuze = vierkant
        repeat 4 times
            forward 50
            turn 90
        forward 50
    if vormkeuze = driehoek
        repeat 3 times
            forward 67
            turn 120
        forward 67
    if vormkeuze = cirkel
        repeat 60 times
            forward 4
            turn 6
        forward 4
    if vormkeuze = zeshoek
        repeat 6 times
            forward 33
            turn 60
        forward 33
    if vormkeuze = ster
        turn 80
        repeat 5 times
            forward 30
            turn -80
            forward 30
            turn 152
        turn -80
    if vormkeuze = ruit
        turn 60
        forward 30
        turn 60
        forward 30
        turn 120
        forward 30
        turn 60
        forward 30
        turn 60
    if vormkeuze = ovaal
        repeat 2 times
            for i in range 1 to 10
                forward i
                turn 9
            for i in range 10 to 1
                forward i
                turn 9
    color white
    forward 60

        print drinken

                prijs = prijs + 1
        if drinken is fanta

        if drinken is sprite
                prijs = prijs + 1
        eten = ask 'Wat wilt u daarbij eten, u heb de keuze uit een kroket, frikandel of een kaassoufflé?'
        print eten
        if eten is kroket
                prijs = prijs + 2
        if eten is frikandel
                prijs = prijs + 2
        if eten is kaassoufflé
                prijs = prijs + 2
        fruit = ask 'Wilt u daar nog fruit bij? Zo ja, wat voor een soort fruit zo u willen u kan kiezen uit een appel een banaan of een aardbei?'
        print fruit
        if fruit is appel
                prijs = prijs + 3
        if fruit is banaan
                prijs = prijs + 3
        if fruit is aardbei
                prijs = prijs + 3
        kortingscode = ask 'Heeft u nog een kortingscode?'
        print kortingscode
        if kortingscode is hallo
                prijs = prijs -3
        print 'Dat is dan ' prijs ' euro'
        print 'Eet smakelijk'

        if q is paper
            if com is rock
                print 'Congrats man! You win'
                y = y + 1

                print 'Ouch ! Computer Won.'
        if com is paper
            if q is rock
                print 'Computer Won.'
            if q is scissors
                print 'You won'
                y = y+1
        if q is scissors
            if com is rock
                print 'Computer Won by an Inch. '
        if com is scissors
            if q is rock
                print 'You Won'
                y = y+1

# Draw tree with turtle. Use backtracking with lists
# Use programmers mode for unclipped drawing.
# Setup the parameters
basic_length = 200
current_length = 0
# The minium length has to match with one of the calculate lengths
# for at level 10 we do not have < as compare operator.
minium_length = 7 # Do not draw below this length.
factor_num = 7
factor_den = 16  # This gives .75 % reduction at each level.
branch_factor = 5  # The 180/5 angle between branches.
colors = red, green, blue, black, purple
# Bias the branches from a knot.
angle_variation = 0, -15, -30, 0, 15, 30
stack = 1,2
remove 1 from stack
remove 2 from stack
# Push on stack [length, #branch, #anglevariation] kind of lists.
# When we had 'while' we could use a sentinel. Now we have to estimate the
# number of iterations.
sentinel = -1, -1, 0
add sentinel to stack
# First go to bottom of screen for nice root of three.
i = 0 - basic_length
forward i
forward basic_length
# Push root's 'last branch'
list_tmp = 1,2
remove 1 from list_tmp
remove 2 from list_tmp
add basic_length to list_tmp
add 0 to list_tmp
add 0 to list_tmp
add list_tmp to stack
# Initialize loop variables.
current_branch = branch_factor
current_length = basic_length * factor_num / factor_den
current_angle = angle_variation at random
track_back = 0
repeat 200 times  # You need to guess this number
    if current_length = minium_length # Carefull here we have no < jet !!!!
        color colors at random
        track_back = 1
    if track_back = 1
        list_tmp = 1,2
        remove 1 from list_tmp
        remove 2 from list_tmp
        first = 1
        last_lst = 0
        for lst in stack
            if first = 0
                add last_lst to list_tmp
            else
                first = 0
            last_lst = lst
        stack = list_tmp
        i = 1
        for elem in last_lst
            if i = 1
                current_length = elem
            if i = 2
                current_branch = elem
            if i = 3
                current_angle = elem
            i = i + 1
        len = 0 - current_length
        forward len
    drawline = 1
    track_back = 0
    new_angle = 0
    if current_branch = branch_factor # Start at op of new branch
        a = 90 - 180 / branch_factor / 2 + current_angle
        turn a
        new_angle = 1
    else
        if current_branch = 0 # All branches have been drawn
            a = 90 -180 / branch_factor / 2 - current_angle
            turn a
            drawline = 0
            track_back = 1
        else # Draw intermediate branch
            a = -180 / branch_factor
            turn a
    if drawline = 1
        forward current_length
        b = current_branch - 1
        list_tmp = 1,2
        remove 1 from list_tmp
        remove 2 from list_tmp
        add current_length to list_tmp
        add b to list_tmp
        add current_angle to list_tmp
        add list_tmp to stack
        current_length = current_length * factor_num / factor_den
        current_branch = branch_factor
    if new_angle = 1
        current_angle = angle_variation at random
